snippet: Se Ri Pak is retiring after the season, ending a Hall of Fame career that inspired a wave of South Korean players who followed her to the L.P.G.A. Tour.
abstract: South Korean Hall of Fame golfer Se Ri Pak shoots three-under-par 69 at JTBC Founders Cup in Phoenix before announcing she will retire after season.
lead_paragraph: Se Ri Pak is retiring after the season, ending a Hall of Fame career that inspired a wave of South Korean players who followed her to the L.P.G.A. Tour.
